{"lemma":"لُجَّةٍ","slug":"لُجَّةٍ","root":"ل.ج.ج","root_slug":"ل-ج-ج","root_link":"/words/roots/ل-ج-ج","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"لُجَّةٍ","root":"لجج","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n37551","n37552"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%84%D9%8F%D8%AC%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be stubborn, to be obstinate"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to insist, to be pertinacious, to be dogged"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to persist, to continue"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to bother, to pester"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to weaken, to exhaust, to harass"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"chasm, gulf; gap","examples":[{"text":"اعلن مدير اعلام شرطة قيادة محافظة واسط، حسن عواد، اليوم الجمعة، ضبط شرطة المحافظة نحو الف حبة مخدرة في سيطرة اللج كانت مخفية بداخل محرك سيارة.","english":"The Press Director of the Police Headquarters of the Province of Wāsiṭ, Hasan ʿuwād, has announced that on Friday the police of the province has seized around a thousand narcotic pills in the control of a gap hidden in the interior of a car engine."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"abyss, depth of the sea"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/lad͡ʒ.d͡ʒa/","/lud͡ʒd͡ʒ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n37551","headword_ar":"لَجَّةٌ","root":"lj","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Voices, cries, clamour, confused noise,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a mixture of voices,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,) of men, (S,) and sometimes of camels. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K"]},{"entry_id":"n37552","headword_ar":"لُجَّةٌ","root":"lj","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luj~N","text_ar":"لُجٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"main body"},{"kind":"text","text":"of water, (S, K,) or of the sea: [the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deep:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"depth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deep,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the sea,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of which the bottom cannot be reached;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fathomless deep:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luj~apN","text_ar":"لُجَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baHorK","text_ar":"بَحْرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luj~u","text_ar":"لُجُّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a great expanse of water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sea, of which the extremities cannot be seen:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luj~N","text_ar":"لُجٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lujajN","text_ar":"لُجَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lijaAjN","text_ar":"لِجَاجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; the last pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luj~apN","text_ar":"لُجَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN luj~apN waAsiEapN","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ لُجَّةٌ وَاسِعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is a wide fathomless deep"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: a phrase by which one is likened to a sea, in amplitude. (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaA^an~a","text_ar":"كَاَنَّ"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2651},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eayonahu luj~apN","text_ar":"عَيْنَهُ لُجَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"As though his eye were a fathomless sea"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intensely black."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlZ~uEonu tasobaHu","text_ar":"الظُّعْنُ تَسْبَحُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~araAbi","text_ar":"السَّرَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY luj~i","text_ar":"فِى لُجِّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The women in the camel-litters swim in the great expanse of mirage."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luj~apu AlZ~alaAmi","text_ar":"لُجَّةُ الظَّلَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The depth of the darkness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"All~ayoli","text_ar":"اللَّيْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luj~u","text_ar":"لُجُّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The depth of night; its intense darkness and blackness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamalu A^adohamu luj~N","text_ar":"جَمَلُ اَدْهَمُ لُجٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A deep black,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intensely black, camel."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luj~apN","text_ar":"لُجَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luj~N","text_ar":"لُجٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A numerous assembly, company, troop,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"congregated body:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luj~apN","text_ar":"لُجَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"with reference to the sea. (TA.) ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luj~apN A^amorK","text_ar":"لُجَّةٌ اَمْرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The main part of an affair."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","L","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}